## What this doc doesn't cover

- **Encrypted backups.** Use `restic` or `borgbackup` if you need at-rest encryption.
- **Point-in-time restore.** Not worth the complexity at this scale.
- **Cross-version restore.** Restore against the same {{project_name}} version you backed up from. If you must cross versions, restore first, then upgrade — never the other way around.
